    "Despite variations in technological capacity, socio-economic conditions, and governance structures, several common themes emerge.",
    "These shared patterns provide valuable insights for other developing nations seeking to modernize their legal frameworks through digitization.",
    "Key Challenges Across Case Studies• Infrastructure Gaps.",
    "A recurring challenge in most countries, particularly in rural or underserved areas, is inadequate digital infrastructure.",
